title: Salmon and Cheddar quiche
ingredients: ['225g Cheddar cheese, cubed', '1/4 onion, diced', '4 eggs', '350ml evaporated milk', '1 pinch salt', '1 pinch ground black pepper', '1 pinch garlic granules', '1 pinch dried parsley', '1 pinch dried sage', '1 (418g) tin salmon, drained, flaked and bones removed', '1 (20cm) pastry case', '60g Cheddar cheese, grated and divided']
